ection":1,"text":", let's see.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.33381,0.059624,0.46533,0.027417,0.022372,0.019258,0.015171,0.014782,0.013194,0.011416,0.010024,0.0076064],"unified_progress":[0.20783,0.054635,0.55321,0.035956,0.03015,0.026252,0.022028,0.02008,0.017005,0.012789,0.010592,0.0094722]},{"section":2,"text":"The patient is a 40-year-old woman with a several-year history of widespread body pain and stiffness, mainly in the shoulders, upper back, hips, thighs, and knees.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.17155,0.32,0.078217,0.11623,0.066631,0.065215,0.04556,0.037367,0.030897,0.026218,0.022375,0.019744],"unified_progress":[0.19876,0.18712,0.091667,0.1158,0.082445,0.083593,0.058648,0.05052,0.042996,0.036186,0.030128,0.022133]},{"section":3,"text":"She also has fatigue, increased need for sleep (14 hours but low quality), cognitive issues like feeling \"not all there,\" and some physical exam findings.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.15355,0.26067,0.17911,0.077231,0.059157,0.073218,0.042227,0.057719,0.030893,0.026219,0.021562,0.018446],"unified_progress":[0.13107,0.17684,0.1312,0.10297,0.079747,0.086753,0.06146,0.076099,0.049387,0.042355,0.035407,0.026714]},{"section":4,"text":"Her vital signs are mostly normal except maybe the blood pressure is a bit low (58 diastolic?), but not sure if that's significant.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.092159,0.15584,0.1449,0.11297,0.091267,0.085849,0.072672,0.069684,0.055986,0.04733,0.040499,0.030841],"unified_progress":[0.08097,0.1217,0.11099,0.10891,0.10346,0.095866,0.085139,0.080036,0.06839,0.059771,0.049499,0.035277]},{"section":5,"text":"No joint deformities or swelling, which is important.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.070057,0.12462,0.11782,0.10276,0.092618,0.091121,0.083072,0.081336,0.073682,0.063878,0.055479,0.043557],"unified_progress":[0.065867,0.1013,0.098366,0.10085,0.099345,0.095664,0.091042,0.088641,0.082281,0.074056,0.060199,0.04239]},{"section":6,"text":"First, the key points here are the chronic, widespread pain and stiffness without joint swelling or deformities.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.06012,0.10815,0.11465,0.10788,0.096413,0.086725,0.081057,0.0775,0.071014,0.075678,0.062327,0.058479],"unified_progress":[0.057674,0.082952,0.087579,0.09607,0.095041,0.093391,0.095498,0.09061,0.085384,0.087514,0.072138,0.056148]},{"section":7,"text":"That makes me think of fibromyalgia because it's known for widespread musculoskeletal pain and tenderness without inflammation.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.049426,0.09187,0.10524,0.10839,0.10292,0.093134,0.08873,0.081968,0.074136,0.077909,0.063865,0.062411],"unified_progress":[0.048829,0.069776,0.084267,0.093037,0.096072,0.09932,0.097524,0.094702,0.089344,0.090424,0.075113,0.061593]},{"section":8,"text":"The fatigue and cognitive symptoms (like \"brain fog\") are also common in fibromyalgia.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.046554,0.087656,0.095077,0.097277,0.096517,0.094022,0.091973,0.088292,0.081546,0.081854,0.072164,0.067068],"unified_progress":[0.047169,0.06997,0.078661,0.085466,0.090594,0.095758,0.095011,0.096412,0.093643,0.094444,0.083812,0.06906]},{"section":9,"text":"The patient's sleep issues, even though she's sleeping a lot, the quality is poor, which aligns with the non-restorative sleep seen in fibro.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.056272,0.10034,0.095546,0.09034,0.089416,0.092395,0.089595,0.089853,0.082091,0.078917,0.071785,0.063447],"unified_progress":[0.056953,0.082541,0.082218,0.083366,0.087486,0.091922,0.09113,0.09418,0.09092,0.089987,0.082355,0.06694]},{"section":10,"text":"Other possibilities to consider: lupus or other autoimmune conditions, but those usually have joint swelling, rashes, or other symptoms.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025924,0.060969,0.078502,0.089318,0.094881,0.096535,0.10318,0.10201,0.098897,0.097564,0.087924,0.064296],"unified_progress":[0.028714,0.057972,0.074578,0.083934,0.095003,0.097501,0.10197,0.10481,0.10324,0.10809,0.088273,0.055913]},{"section":11,"text":"Rheumatoid arthritis would have morning stiffness and swollen joints.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025526,0.059979,0.074069,0.085411,0.093884,0.099267,0.10515,0.10458,0.10046,0.09811,0.087116,0.066455],"unified_progress":[0.036442,0.058138,0.07401,0.084494,0.093967,0.10148,0.10257,0.10605,0.10347,0.10278,0.082857,0.053745]},{"section":12,"text":"Since there's no swelling or redness here, that's less likely.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024552,0.058518,0.07293,0.0818,0.087571,0.093164,0.10146,0.10462,0.1053,0.1024,0.095588,0.072107],"unified_progress":[0.028845,0.057865,0.072317,0.081554,0.092396,0.094869,0.10021,0.10568,0.10603,0.11199,0.089439,0.058816]},{"section":13,"text":"Hypothyroidism can cause fatigue and weight gain, but she might have other symptoms like cold intolerance.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.0231,0.055074,0.068646,0.079136,0.088144,0.096039,0.10448,0.10768,0.10584,0.10471,0.096581,0.070577],"unified_progress":[0.034936,0.058874,0.071202,0.078839,0.089715,0.095761,0.10028,0.10674,0.10616,0.11041,0.090603,0.056478]},{"section":14,"text":"The vitals don't show a high temperature, so infection is less likely.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025396,0.059245,0.073994,0.082477,0.08786,0.092964,0.1017,0.10471,0.10444,0.102,0.095766,0.069448],"unified_progress":[0.030243,0.06148,0.076004,0.08382,0.094536,0.095831,0.10105,0.10441,0.10368,0.10724,0.087728,0.053979]},{"section":15,"text":"Chronic fatigue syndrome could be a consideration, but fibromyalgia often overlaps with that.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022401,0.054069,0.069815,0.080956,0.0895,0.095156,0.10216,0.1046,0.10248,0.10404,0.095546,0.079278],"unified_progress":[0.032646,0.057297,0.070966,0.080963,0.089115,0.095202,0.09969,0.10379,0.10247,0.10636,0.092142,0.069367]},{"section":16,"text":"The pain on palpation in specific muscles (deltoids, trapezius, etc.) might relate to trigger points, which are part of fibromyalgia criteria.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038021,0.076369,0.08204,0.086715,0.09022,0.09471,0.096043,0.095134,0.096131,0.089294,0.081167,0.074155],"unified_progress":[0.043124,0.070619,0.081587,0.089997,0.094989,0.098576,0.097654,0.096999,0.096749,0.088066,0.077646,0.063993]},{"section":17,"text":"The American College of Rheumatology criteria for fibromyalgia include widespread pain index and symptom severity, along with other symptoms like fatigue, sleep disturbance, and cognitive symptoms.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036754,0.071838,0.079919,0.086307,0.092135,0.095584,0.097606,0.095973,0.091282,0.091088,0.083331,0.078182],"unified_progress":[0.04089,0.064616,0.078354,0.085497,0.091399,0.10131,0.098208,0.098001,0.094765,0.091953,0.08338,0.07163]},{"section":18,"text":"Since she has multiple of these, it's pointing towards fibromyalgia.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036178,0.07388,0.089149,0.093041,0.090529,0.086101,0.086483,0.085112,0.084306,0.090983,0.084402,0.099836],"unified_progress":[0.035181,0.059124,0.068663,0.08039,0.082933,0.086704,0.088845,0.092505,0.09383,0.099989,0.10317,0.10867]},{"section":19,"text":"The absence of inflammatory signs (no swelling, normal ESR/CRP if done) would support that it's not an inflammatory arthritis.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034712,0.073818,0.087959,0.093004,0.093956,0.093579,0.096619,0.094346,0.092189,0.087999,0.082752,0.069068],"unified_progress":[0.034758,0.06667,0.081715,0.088648,0.096221,0.095935,0.098591,0.097026,0.096232,0.094363,0.084544,0.065296]},{"section":20,"text":"So putting it all together, the most likely diagnosis is fibromyalgia.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026911,0.054116,0.066216,0.072504,0.076604,0.079158,0.08397,0.087007,0.091695,0.096817,0.10515,0.15986],"unified_progress":[0.02497,0.039225,0.047897,0.058882,0.062871,0.07162,0.076202,0.087442,0.096799,0.10692,0.13971,0.18746]}]}}